        \PYG{n}{knowledge\PYGZus{}retrieval\PYGZus{}instruction} \PYG{o}{=} \PYG{l+s+s1}{\PYGZsq{}Retrieve relevant information from a knowledge base that can assist in refining the solution.\PYGZsq{}}
